tips.01=Settle on a biome without extreme temperature
tips.02=Everything takes a good amount of time, try to multitask when you are waiting for something
tips.03=Read the questbook, its your best friend and only guide
tips.04=Ancient ruins can provide you with some really good items
tips.05=Expect realistic ratios from the crafts
tips.06=Once you find a ore vein you will enough of that material for a long time
tips.07=Try to find clever solutions, the questbook only shows you the tools, find your own path
